HEADWORD: Sheepbite
<hw>Sheep"bite`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To bite or
nibble like a sheep; hence, to practice petty thefts.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
